{"tid":346013,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手養貓 有冇好既貓砂貓糧推薦","createTime":"2017-08-03T14:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T13:59:34.000Z","uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b460fa9c92958fbf32d2860991eda8ad0e462f","tid":346013,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"過幾日接佢番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb110f1b8e4803d6ba4ebc6b453707c12a165f7","tid":346013,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"[membertg: nnnnntc][/member]<br />\n養緊好多貓 睇下有冇野解答到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f32165aed763d91547c042662d3e1af3924885e","tid":346013,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"豆腐砂"},{"pid":"cff6accf53180fd0e9865c2eab3c461abe3e60c3","tid":346013,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T20:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://a.ecimg.tw/items/DEAK68A9005DH9P/000001_1487727359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa.ecimg.tw%2Fitems%2FDEAK68A9005DH9P%2F000001_1487727359.jpg&h=26e47eb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b7798f17adbafcf1b3f29e689e0977874c2f059","tid":346013,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T21:58:01.000Z","msg":"開始用豆腐砂實冇死 n1算平靚正 用落左就會知度自己想要d咩效果而睇下轉唔轉砂<br />\n<br />\n貓糧既話可以參考之前個貓糧資料庫 d資料幾齊幾中肯<br />\n睇budget 間最好都一日最少一餐糧頭依d濕食<br />\n因為長期食乾糧水份會唔夠 長遠影響健康<br />\n水機個d只可以係輔助 直接係飲食涉取就唔洗成日怕佢飲唔夠水<br />\n同埋避免比魚類 食耐左上癮就難戒 同埋都比其他肉類冇咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d74b623be43cda54de03e818e526ed4227b480","tid":346013,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T09:45:59.000Z","msg":"睇budget <br />\n錢ok既用小白/豆之<br />\n平既用n1<br />\n糧分呢幾類<br />\n生肉<br />\nfreeze dried <br />\nFrozen <br />\nHome made<br />\n價錢由貴到平<br />\nCan<br />\n睇食咩牌子，價錢大同小異。<br />\n乾糧<br />\n貴既orijen Nv ultimate protein<br />\n平既幾平都有"},{"pid":"09a0e8a5613d5f8eeb8066d3e55a434801859849","tid":346013,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T20:36:28.000Z","msg":"買左小白砂<br />\n同 pro plan bb糧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c233831d1c729054073058eee327282d3280d31","tid":346013,"uid":79449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"⼃<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/125409_c463a24ef7c649163b2814279dc33720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F125409_c463a24ef7c649163b2814279dc33720.jpg&h=ef083777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用緊呢隻，都淨係用過呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d98d900eae26d35fc0973af7e79efae1a4026a","tid":346013,"uid":83321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:26:57.000Z","msg":"用紙砂 豆腐砂方便啲就咁沖落廁所就得"},{"pid":"165678a6ddcd8f8d1ffe24148640f64ead1b32c0","tid":346013,"uid":45526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買左小白砂<br />\n同 pro plan bb糧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nProplan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵啲肉類蛋白高啲既糧 <br />\n由細開始俾佢學下食主食罐<br />\n唔怕轉食有困難 唔係大左你想佢戒乾糧轉其他都難"},{"pid":"e8cd1af1bd6ad8ebb5ca3984cff80f43d8cd8f85","tid":346013,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用紙砂 豆腐砂方便啲就咁沖落廁所就得</blockquote><br />\n我而家都改左當垃圾咁倒，太大舊之餘住緊嗰度樓齡高驚塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad55676797d8710f341ea361ccf4da35b29e8ae","tid":346013,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"用緊n1 都ok"},{"pid":"3697b57ab68cc654203ffeb06095074b0ff16768","tid":346013,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"小白凝結同吸味好過n1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但貴少少"},{"pid":"44c3140f5241f7e86327ef8f8c81b808dc882c73","tid":346013,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:52:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小白凝結同吸味好過n1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但貴少少</blockquote><br />\n小白隻雲呢拿味好難聞"},{"pid":"7de00aa7997a4e8ad01ec59aab6d650d2e936d01","tid":346013,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"報紙撕到一條條就得"},{"pid":"d9f17cb4d80e828a9e1d5b862f6728983f2b2872","tid":346013,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>⼃<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/125409_c463a24ef7c649163b2814279dc33720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F125409_c463a24ef7c649163b2814279dc33720.jpg&h=ef083777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用緊呢隻，都淨係用過呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab0d40e35178016bcef0388bad366e0ff85c6e6","tid":346013,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報紙撕到一條條就得</blockquote><br />\n佢bb 個時係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243dde8522f69e82ea57be8e5791f9c24cb42bde","tid":346013,"uid":92600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小白凝結同吸味好過n1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但貴少少</blockquote><br />\n小白隻雲呢拿味好難聞</blockquote><br />\n開頭都覺 好假<br />\n但n1吸唔曬屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}